channel.title: Cache Packing 474 Client?
channel.description:
Hey, I have not been around RSPS's a long ass time. I'd like to know how I can cache pack a 474 client (Rs2-Server).
I need to fix my maps, Also I want to add newer items such as d-claws and spirit shields to the the server.
Example of my messed up maps. [url=http://prntscr.com/4g5wux]Screenshot by Lightshot[/url]
Will rep++

item.title: Cache Packing 474 Client?
item.dc:creator: @codyorr4 codyorr4
item.description:
@codyorr4 wrote:

Most should pack once you’ve ran the server.

for items you’ll most likely need itembonuspacker.bat

and for names/color/ints

frostcache editor.
which can pack most things, i believe.
npcs, objects, items, others.
